Matthew Beard (English actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matthew_Beard_(English_actor) 0 Matthew Beard (born 25 March 1989) is an English film and television actor, and model, best known for his role as Blake Morrison in the 2007 film And When Did You Last See Your Father?
